warm_up_card.Title: Warm Up Card
warm_up_card.Description: A warm up is a must before getting into any physical battle! This card teaches you "Warm Up" skill.

power_blow_card.Title: Power Blow Card
power_blow_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Power Blow" skill to attack the enemy by winding around it using my flexibility. The skill musters up the power condensed in the body.

dodge_master_card.Title: Dodge Master Card
dodge_master_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the "Dodge Master" skill used to avoid opponents' attack.

galder_thrower_card.Title: Galder Thrower Card
galder_thrower_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Galder Thrower" skill which causes damage to the enemy by throwing 100 Galder.

magic_meltdown_card.Title: Magic Meltdown Card
magic_meltdown_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Magic Meltdown" skill. It stops magical power for a certain period of time by breaking the ball containing the enemy's magical power.

magic_defense_breaker_card.Title: Magic Defense Breaker Card
magic_defense_breaker_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the "Magic Defense Breaker" skill. It takes away magical protective curtain surrounding the enemy to reduce the magical Defense Power for a certain period of time.

mana_reflector_card.Title: Mana Reflector Card
mana_reflector_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Mana Reflector". It reduces damage caused by magic spell and project the magic power back to the enemy by creating a reflecting shield.

shield_all_card.Title: Shield All Card
shield_all_card.Description: Card No. 7 teaches the "Shield All" skill. It increases My Defense Power along with that of the surrounding Party members for a certain period of time.

sturdy_shield_card.Title: Sturdy Shield Card
sturdy_shield_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the "Sturdy Shield" skill. It increases Defense Power for a certain period of time by attaching the fine threads around Me to the shiel and spinning them using a special skill.

titanium_wrist_card.Title: Titanium Wrist Card
titanium_wrist_card.Description: Card No. 3 teaches the "Titanium Wrist" skill which enhances the Power Blow skill.

skunk_pouch_card.Title: Skunk Pouch Card
skunk_pouch_card.Description: Carn No. 6 teaches the "Skunk Pouch" skill used to faint the enemy temporarily by throwing a pouch with a bad skunk smell in it.

physical_training_card.Title: Physical Training Card
physical_training_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Physical Training" skill to increase My HP trough physical training.

final_blow_card.Title: Final Blow Card
final_blow_card.Description: Card No. 13 teaches the "Final Blow" skill used to deliver a powerful attack by venting wrath in the mind.

volley_kick_card.Title: Volley Kick Card
volley_kick_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the "Volley Kick" skill. It kicks the enemy upwards using flexibility of one's torso.

galder_barrage_card.Title: Galder Barrage Card
galder_barrage_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the "Galder Barrage" skill. This is a wide-range skill throwing 150 galders in three seperate directions.

team_bolster_card.Title: Team Bolster Card
team_bolster_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Team Bolster" skill. This skill suppliments "Shield All" skill to raise defense power of you and your party members that are close by.

siren_song_card.Title: Siren Song Card
siren_song_card.Description: Teaches the skill Siren Song. It damages the enemy with the power of your voice.

evolution_card.Title: Evolution Card
evolution_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Evolution" that morphs the user into a beast.

beast_claw_card.Title: Beast Claw Card
beast_claw_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Beast Claw" that delivers a devastating blow to the enemy.

fatal_wound_card.Title: Fatal Wound Card
fatal_wound_card.Description: This skill can only be used with 'Evolution' and will deal continuous damage to the enemy.

fist_full_of_galders_card.Title: Fist Full of Galders Card
fist_full_of_galders_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches "Fist Full of Galders" which is known to be extra painful for both player and the target due to the fact that the playerhas to let go of their hard earned 300 Galder.

sumo_suit_card.Title: Sumo Suit Card
sumo_suit_card.Prerequisite Skills: Shield All Lv.10Sturdy Shield LV. 10Physical Training Lv. 10
sumo_suit_card.Description: Card No. 13 teaches the "Sumo Suit" skill. It turns the user's body fat and doubles it to become padding againstpower attacks.

deadly_funk_card.Title: Deadly Funk Card
deadly_funk_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches you Deadly Funk which knocks your enemies out with it's horrible smell.

card_strike_card.Title: Card Strike Card
card_strike_card.Description: Card No.8 teaches the "Card Strike" skill. It attacks the enemy by holding the Empty Card between two fingers and throwing them using wrist flexibility.

super_hips_card.Title: Super Hips Card
super_hips_card.Description: An assisting skill for Dodge Master. Card No. 3 teaches the "Super Hips" skill which helps one to avoid Critical Attacks and Power Attacks from monsters that are in similar level as the player.

bodyguard_card.Title: Bodyguard Card
bodyguard_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches "Bodyguard" skill. This skill allows the user to sacrifice their health and take part of the party members' damage.

impelling_rage_card.Title: Impelling Rage Card
impelling_rage_card.Description: This Card teaches the skill "Impelling Rage" that damages and pushes the enemies around the player.

furious_galder_throw_card.Title: Furious Galder Throw Card
furious_galder_throw_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches "Furious Galder Throw" which deals either very low damage or very high damage by throwing 500 galder at the target.

flux_capacitor_card.Title: Flux Capacitor Card
flux_capacitor_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches you the 2Flux Capacitor2 skill. It consumes HP to fill up MP.

metamorphosis_card.Title: Metamorphosis Card
metamorphosis_card.Description: This Card teaches the skill 'Metamorphosis' which is exclusive to a Racoon.

wild_nail_card.Title: Wild Nail Card
wild_nail_card.Description: This card teaches 'Wild Nail' which deals a big physical damage.

one_pair_card.Title: One Pair Card
one_pair_card.Description: Teaches the skill One Pair. It throws a pair of cards at a single target.

lady_luck_card.Title: Lady Luck Card
lady_luck_card.Description: Card No.7 teaches you Lady Luck which increases the number of cards that can be thrown in a One Pair.

sharp_scream_card.Title: Sharp Scream Card
sharp_scream_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the skill 'Sharp Scream' which inflicts damage to nearby enemies by screaming loudly. Must be in a transformed state to use.

2_hit_combo_card.Title: 2 Hit Combo Card
2_hit_combo_card.Description: Punch and kick combo. Skill Card No. 12.

raging_nail_card.Title: Raging Nail Card
raging_nail_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches you 'Raging Nail'. You use Wild Mutation in order to use this skill.

entrancing_wink_card.Title: Entrancing Wink Card
entrancing_wink_card.Prerequisite Skills: Magic Meltdown Lv. 10Magic Defense Breaker Lv. 10
entrancing_wink_card.Description: Confuse your enemiesto prevent them from using Magic-Type skills for a short period of time. Skill Card No. 13.

power_charging_card.Title: Power Charging Card
power_charging_card.Description: Deals a massive blow and freezes enemies, rendering them unable to move. Skill Card No. 10.

heavy_hit_card.Title: Heavy Hit Card
heavy_hit_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches you 'Heavy Hit' to push the enemies way!

full_house_card.Title: Full House Card
full_house_card.Description: Use 5 cards to attack your enemy. If you fail to do damage you will receive damage instead. Skill Card No. 7.

summon_card_soldier_card.Title: (Summon) Card Soldier Card
summon_card_soldier_card.Description: Card No. 6 Teaches the skill "[Summon] Card Soldier" which uses an empty card from the inventory to summon a card soldier to attack enemies. Must be in a transformed state.

stone_shower_card.Title: Stone Shower Card
stone_shower_card.Description: This skill uses the earth around you to shower your enemy with deadly Stone Shower.

invincible_drill_card.Title: Invincible Drill Card
invincible_drill_card.Description: Passive. Card No.6 shows how to learn the "Invincible Drill" skill. It keeps concentration on drilling even if someone interrupts.

gun_carrier_card.Title: Gun Carrier Card
gun_carrier_card.Description: Gun Carrier is a required skill before wielding any gun in Trickster Online.

sixth_sense_card.Title: Sixth Sense Card
sixth_sense_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Sixth Sense" skill. It increases Sensing Power for a certain period of time to detect any changes in your surroundings.

stone_strike_card.Title: Stone Strike Card
stone_strike_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Stone Strike" skill. It is designed to deal a blow to the enemy by sensing the weakness of them and the flow of the surrounding power.

heavy_carrier_card.Title: Heavy Carrier Card
heavy_carrier_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Heavy Carrier" skill. It creates a space to store something.

shuriken_master_card.Title: Shuriken Master Card
shuriken_master_card.Description: Card No. 7 teaches the "Shuriken Master" skill which causes damage to the enemy by throwing the weapon.

invincible_reload_card.Title: Invincible Reload Card
invincible_reload_card.Description: Invincible Reload will allow your character to plow through and keep on reloading the gun.

sticky_foot_card.Title: Sticky Foot Card
sticky_foot_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the "Sticky Foot" skill. It reduces the enemy's Dodging Power for a certain period of time by pouring sticky oil onto the floor where the enemy moves around.

gun_booster_card.Title: Gun Booster Card
gun_booster_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Gun Booster" skill which increases the level of damage when using guns to attack.

basic_detection_card.Title: Basic Detection Card
basic_detection_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the "Basic Detection" skill used to find out the existence of any items underground within a 80m range.

armor_destructor_card.Title: Armor Destructor Card
armor_destructor_card.Description: Card No. 1 teaches the "Armor Destructor" skill. It reduces the enemy's Defense Power for a certain period of time by destroying the enemy's armor or its strong outer shell.

quick_reload_card.Title: Quick Reload Card
quick_reload_card.Description: Card No. 2 teaches the "Quick Reload" skill which allows loading while moving.

lucky_seven_card.Title: Lucky Seven Card
lucky_seven_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the "Lucky Seven" skill. It increases luck for a certain period of time using the fairy of luck's power.

anger_management_card.Title: Anger Management Card
anger_management_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches you the Anger Management skill. In increases the rate at which your Stress Points are accumulated in order to activate the Crazy Drilling skill.

compound_master_card.Title: Compound Master Card
compound_master_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Compound Master" skill. It raises the applicability of the maturing compound.

precise_pitch_card.Title: Precise Pitch Card
precise_pitch_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches the "Precise Pitch" skill. It strengthens Attack Power of the throwing weapons for a certain period of time.

item_detector_card.Title: Item Detector Card
item_detector_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Item Detector" skill. Skill can detect the existence of items in a certain range in a certain area.

aura_of_luck_card.Title: Aura of Luck Card
aura_of_luck_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Aura of Luck" skill. This skill enables an aura to raise luck on you and to your party members.

chain_of_knives_card.Title: Chain of Knives Card
chain_of_knives_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches you Chain of Knives which allows you to throw multiple knives at a single target.

mega_crazy_drilling_card.Title: Mega Crazy Drilling Card
mega_crazy_drilling_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches you the Mega Crazy Drilling skill. It maintains Crazy Drill mode by increasing the anger and changing it into a strong will which increases the duration of the skill.

gas_mask_card.Title: Gas Mask Card
gas_mask_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Gas Mask" skill. It gives the user and the nearby user's party a defense against the skunk pouch skill.

landmine_card.Title: Landmine Card
landmine_card.Description: Teaches the skill Landmine. It places a power proximity mine.

sticky_icky_card.Title: Sticky Icky Card
sticky_icky_card.Description: With 'Sticky Icky,' you can make enemies around you very unfortunate.

lightning_rod_card.Title: Lightning Rod Card
lightning_rod_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Lightning Rod" skill. It decreases the electric attacks that the user and the party may come in contact with. Party members must be nearby to recieve the effect.

pouch_of_pain_card.Title: Pouch of Pain Card
pouch_of_pain_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Pouch of Pain" that crushes the enemies around the user with the weight of the pouch.

fan_of_knives_card.Title: Fan of Knives Card
fan_of_knives_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches "Fan of Knives" which enables the player to throw several shurikens to multiple targets.

butt_plate_card.Title: Butt Plate Card
butt_plate_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Butt Plate" skill. It attacks the enemy in a close distance using a butt plate of a rifle. This skill can only be used when the gun is mounted.

power_shot_card.Title: Power Shot Card
power_shot_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the "Power Shot" skill which causes a sever damage as the bullet carries strong energy.

shooting_spree_card.Title: Shooting Spree Card
shooting_spree_card.Description: Card No. 3 teaches the "Shooting Spree" skill which fires guns randomly without targeting a specific enemy to damage unspecified opponents.

lucky_fist_card.Title: Lucky Fist Card
lucky_fist_card.Description: Teaches the skill Lucky Fist. A desperate blow that leaves everything to one's luck.

lock-on_card.Title: Lock-on Card
lock-on_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches you Lock-On which lowers your target's HV.

double_shot_card.Title: Double Shot Card
double_shot_card.Description: You can shoot 2 shots in a row with 'Double Shot'.

shield_breaker_card.Title: Shield Breaker Card
shield_breaker_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Shield Breaker" skill. The skill is so strong it can break through all shields and Sumo Suit skills.

leg_training_card.Title: Leg Training Card
leg_training_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches "Leg Training" which increases immunity to movement impairing attacks of the party members by strengthening their legs.

explosives_expert_card.Title: Explosives Expert Card
explosives_expert_card.Description: This skill will let you plant land mines for a short period of time. Skill Card No. 6.

poison_pouch_card.Title: Poison Pouch Card
poison_pouch_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches you 'Poison Pouch' to add a touch of poison to Pouch of Pain.

hide_card.Title: Hide Card
hide_card.Description: You can hide from an enemy. You can't use any items or skills while hiding. Hide will be cancelled when a skill is used. Skill Card No. 3.

poison_assault_card.Title: Poison Assault Card
poison_assault_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the skill 'Poison Assualt' that can only be used while hidden. It throws a poisoned shuriken at the enemy, who when struck will lose health over time.

strong_mind_card.Title: Strong Mind Card
strong_mind_card.Description: Party skill. Increases resistance against Entrancing Wink. Skill Card No.5

sudden_attack_card.Title: Sudden Attack Card
sudden_attack_card.Description: Sudden Attack can only be used while using hide. Strike your enemy with a surprise. Skill Card No. 4.

revealing_eye_card.Title: Revealing Eye Card
revealing_eye_card.Description: Allows caster to spot enemies using Hide skill. Skill Card No. 6.

berserk_card.Title: Berserk Card
berserk_card.Description: Shoot anything and everything in sight! Skill Card No. 4.

gun_overdrive_card.Title: Gun Overdrive Card
gun_overdrive_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches you 'Gun Overdrive' to raise Gun AP for a limited period of time.

sharp_sense_card.Title: Sharp Sense Card
sharp_sense_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the skill 'Sharp Sense' which increases the gun's critical damage for a short period of time.

magical_soul_card.Title: Magical Soul Card
magical_soul_card.Description: Any aspiring magician would first need to learn 'Magical Soul' with this card.

mana_arrow_card.Title: Mana Arrow Card
mana_arrow_card.Description: No Attribute. Card No. 3 teaches the "Mana Arrow" skill used to conjure magical energy existing in the nature to create magic arrows to attack the enemy.

cure_card.Title: Cure Card
cure_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Cure" skill to relieve fatigue and vitalize the metabolism.

invincible_casting_card.Title: Invincible Casting Card
invincible_casting_card.Description: Passive. Card No. 6 teaches "Invincible Casting" skill. It increases concentration to finish the spell regardless of Sense Breaker.

mana_ring_card.Title: Mana Ring Card
mana_ring_card.Description: No Attribute. Card No. 10 teaches the "Mana Ring" skill. It causes a damage to not only the enemy but its surroundings by creating three magic Rings

bottle_of_mana_card.Title: Bottle of Mana Card
bottle_of_mana_card.Description: Passive. Card No. 7 teaches the "Bottle of Mana" skill. It creats a magic bottle to fill it with Mana, increasing MP's maximum value.

aura_of_mana_card.Title: Aura of Mana Card
aura_of_mana_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the "Aura of Mana" skill. It increases Party member's Mana recovery capability for a certain of time as the magic boosts the activity of the surrounding Mana.

rust_card.Title: Rust Card
rust_card.Description: Card No. 8 teaches the "Rust" magic. It reduces the enemy's Attack Power for a certain period of time by spreading Rust around the enemy which makes it weapon blunt.

mana_web_card.Title: Mana Web Card
mana_web_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the "Mana Web" skill. It reduces the enemy's speed for a certain period of time by surrounding the enemy with the spider web created using Mana.

mana_shield_card.Title: Mana Shield Card
mana_shield_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Mana Shield" skill. It increases magical Defense Power by conjuring up magical energy

mana_storm_card.Title: Mana Storm Card
mana_storm_card.Description: No Attribute. Card No. 9 teaches the "Mana Storm" skill. It attacks the enemy in a certain area with a strong storm by adjusting Mana density in the atmosphere.

mist_of_mana_card.Title: Mist of Mana Card
mist_of_mana_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the "Mist of Mana" skill which increases magic power for a certain period of tie by activating it dormant in the body.

mana_ring_booster_card.Title: Mana Ring Booster Card
mana_ring_booster_card.Description: Card No. 2 teaches the "Mana Ring Booster" skill. It increases the destructive power of the magic ring.

arrow_rush_card.Title: Arrow Rush Card
arrow_rush_card.Description: Card No. 13 teaches the "Arrow Rush" skill. It fires arrows continuously without delay.

bolster_ballad_card.Title: Bolster Ballad Card
bolster_ballad_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches the "Bolster Ballad" skill which calms down Party members' mind and reduces MP consumptions.

seal_of_water_card.Title: Seal of Water Card
seal_of_water_card.Description: Card No.8 teaches the "Seal of Water" skill. It is an initiating skill to learn Water Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill, you cannot learn Seal of Fire and Seal of Earth.

drip_bomb_card.Title: Drip Bomb Card
drip_bomb_card.Description: Water Attribute magic. Card No.9 teaches the "Drip Bomb" which attacks the enemy using huge water cannonballs.

icey_shackles_card.Title: Icey Shackles Card
icey_shackles_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches you Icey Shackles which traps your enemies in chains of ice.

water_web_card.Title: Water Web Card
water_web_card.Description: Teaches the skill Water Web. It brings down the enemy's dexterity when hit with Drip Bomb.

water_shield_card.Title: Water Shield Card
water_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Water Shield' for added water protection.

shard_of_the_glacier_card.Title: Shard of the Glacier Card
shard_of_the_glacier_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the "Shard of the Glacier" skill. The user can summon ice shards from the sky to attack enemies.

seal_of_thunder_card.Title: Seal of Thunder Card
seal_of_thunder_card.Description: Card No.6 teaches the "Seal of Thunder" skill. It is an initiating skill to learn Electric Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill, you cannot learn Seal of Wind and Seal of Earth.

electro_attack_card.Title: Electro Attack Card
electro_attack_card.Description: Electric Attribute magic. Card No.5 teaches the "Electro Attack" skill. It creates and projects electro-sparks to the enemy to cause serial damage to the enemy and others surrounding it.

thunderbolt_card.Title: Thunderbolt Card
thunderbolt_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches you Thunderbolt which strikes enemies with a singel, massive thunderbolt.

electroshock_card.Title: Electroshock Card
electroshock_card.Description: Teaches the skill Electroshock. It immobilizes the enemy that's been struck by Electro Attack.

thunder_shield_card.Title: Thunder Shield Card
thunder_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Thunder Shield' for added electricity protection.

tesla_field_card.Title: Tesla Field Card
tesla_field_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches "Tesla Field" skill. The user gathers the electric particles in the air to throw at the enemy. Also once thrown the area in which it lands turns into an electric field that will damage those who walk int o it.

seal_of_fire_card.Title: Seal of Fire Card
seal_of_fire_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches the "Skill of Fire" skill. It helps to learn Fire Attribute magic. Once you learn the magic, you cannot learn Seal of Water and Seal of Wind.

whirlwind_blaze_card.Title: Whirlwind Blaze Card
whirlwind_blaze_card.Description: Fire Attribute magic. Card No.10 teaches the "Whirlwind Blaze skill which attacks the enemy by creating flames around it.

scorching_earth_card.Title: Scorching Earth Card
scorching_earth_card.Description: Card No.11 teaches you Scorching Earth which deals fire damage over a large area.

incinerate_card.Title: Incinerate Card
incinerate_card.Description: Teaches the skill Incinerate. It causes a fiery explosion that burns any enemy.

fire_shield_card.Title: Fire Shield Card
fire_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Fire Shield' for added fire protection.

phoenix_rising_card.Title: Phoenix Rising Card
phoenix_rising_card.Description: Fire attribute magic. It causes enemies to be under an extreme heat and pressure which causes HP to drop constantly.

seal_of_earth_card.Title: Seal of Earth Card
seal_of_earth_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches the "Seal of Earth" which is an initiating skill to learn Earth Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill, you cannot learn Seal of Water and Seal of Thunder.

cleaving_terra_card.Title: Cleaving Terra Card
cleaving_terra_card.Description: Earth Attribute magic. Card No.4 teaches the "Cleaving Terra" skill attacking the enemy by creating severe cleavages on the ground.

deadly_fen_card.Title: Deadly Fen Card
deadly_fen_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches you Deadly Fen which turns dry land into swamp.

summon_boulder_card.Title: Summon Boulder Card
summon_boulder_card.Description: Teaches the skill Summon Boulder. It summons a giant boulder to crush the enemy.

earth_shield_card.Title: Earth Shield Card
earth_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Earth Shield' for added soil protection.

botulism_cloud_card.Title: Botulism Cloud Card
botulism_cloud_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches "Botulism Cloud" skill. This skill increases the target's attack delay.

seal_of_wind_card.Title: Seal of Wind Card
seal_of_wind_card.Description: Card No. 7 teaches the "Seal of Wind" skill. It is an initiating skill to learn Air Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill, you cannot learn Seal of Thunder and Seal of Fire.

wind_blade_card.Title: Wind Blade Card
wind_blade_card.Description: Air Attribute magic. Card No.6 teaches the "Wind Blade" skill used to attack the enemy by creating a sharp vacuum wind around the caster's body.

tornado_blast_card.Title: Tornado Blast Card
tornado_blast_card.Description: Card No.6 teaches you Tornado Blash which uses tornado-force winds to hit enemies.

whirlwind_card.Title: Whirlwind Card
whirlwind_card.Description: Teaches the skill Whirlwind. It summons multiple tornadoes that will attack anyone in range.

wind_shield_card.Title: Wind Shield Card
wind_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Wind Shield' for added air protection.

razor_gale_card.Title: Razor Gale Card
razor_gale_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the "Razor Gale" skill. It creates a sharp wind boomerang to deal strong blows at the enemy. Can be used for long distances.

hinder_snare_card.Title: Hinder Snare Card
hinder_snare_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches the "Hinder Snare" skill. It ties up the enemy around the caster by using the caster's movement as a bait. Caster will not be able to move while performing this magic.

light_pact_card.Title: Light Pact Card
light_pact_card.Description: Card No.4 teaches the "Light Pact" which is an initiating skill to learn Light Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill,you cannot learn Dark Pact.

arrow_of_light_card.Title: Arrow of Light Card
arrow_of_light_card.Description: Light Attribute magic. Card No.3 teaches the "Arrow of Light" which attacks the enemy with pillars of light striking the enemy from the sky.

catastrophe_heal_card.Title: Catastrophe Heal Card
catastrophe_heal_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches the "Catastrophe Heal" skill. This skill allows you to heal yourself faster in times of danger.

oath_of_light_card.Title: Oath of Light Card
oath_of_light_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches you Oath of Light which restores health.

light_shield_card.Title: Light Shield Card
light_shield_card.Description: This card teaches 'Light Shield' for increased light defense attribute, DP, and MA.

basic_healing_card.Title: Basic Healing Card
basic_healing_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the "Basic Healing" skill. This is the skill you can learn before you change your job to treat all malfunctioning skills.

light_wave_card.Title: Light Wave Card
light_wave_card.Description: Teaches the skill Light Wave. Light. It summons a wave of light that could hit multiple targets.

radiant_strike_card.Title: Radiant Strike Card
radiant_strike_card.Description: This card teaches 'Radiant Strike' which strikes all enemies within range.

hearts_grace_card.Title: Heart's Grace Card
hearts_grace_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Heart's Grace" skill. It recovers the health of the user and the user's party members that are near by.

shield_of_heaven_card.Title: Shield of Heaven Card
shield_of_heaven_card.Description: Card No.8 teaches "Shield of Heaven" which creates a holy protective barrier around the caster.

dark_pact_card.Title: Dark Pact Card
dark_pact_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches the "Dark Pact" skil lwhich is an initiating skill to learn Darkness Attribute magic. Once you learn the skill, you cannot learn Light Pact.

hellfire_card.Title: Hellfire Card
hellfire_card.Description: Darkness Attribute magic using the characteristics of darkness. Card No.11 teaches the "Hellfire" skill which attacks the enemy by creating dark blazes which resembles flame from hell.

wicked_flame_card.Title: Wicked Flame Card
wicked_flame_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches the "Wicked Flame" skill. This passive skill aids the "Hellfire" skill for longer lasting damage.

blood_testament_card.Title: Blood Testament Card
blood_testament_card.Description: Card No.6 teaches you Blood Testament which raises you damage while lowering your health.

dark_distractor_card.Title: Dark Distractor Card
dark_distractor_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Dark Distractor" skill. This skill summons a dark being to slow down the movements of the enemy.

dark_lance_card.Title: Dark Lance Card
dark_lance_card.Description: Teaches the skill Dark Lance. It summons a dark lance that strikes the enemy with devastating effect.

dark_barrier_card.Title: Dark Barrier Card
dark_barrier_card.Description: This card teaches 'Dark Barrier' which raises dark resistance temporarily and reflects incoming attacks physically.

gravity_crush_card.Title: Gravity Crush Card
gravity_crush_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Gravity Crush" that increases the gravity and damage the enemies around the user.

withering_disease_card.Title: Withering Disease Card
withering_disease_card.Description: Card No.12 teaches "Withering Disease" which disables the regen of the target.

aqua_bomb_card.Title: Aqua Bomb Card
aqua_bomb_card.Description: This skill card teaches you Aqua Bomb. Skill Card No. 11.

undines_garden_card.Title: Undine's Garden Card
undines_garden_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Undine's Garden" which targets an area with the power of Undine to decrease their resistance to electrical attribute.

staff_of_thunder_card.Title: Staff of Thunder Card
staff_of_thunder_card.Description: This skill card teaches you Staff of Thunder. Skill Card No. 12.

raions_space_card.Title: Raion's Space Card
raions_space_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches the "Raion's Space" which targets an area with the power of Raion to decrease their resistance to fire attribute.

dragon_storm_card.Title: Dragon Storm Card
dragon_storm_card.Description: This skill card teaches you Dragon Storm. Skill Card No.5

salamanders_territory_card.Title: Salamander's Territory Card
salamanders_territory_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Salamander's Territory" which targets an area with the power of Salamander to decrease their resistance to Soil attribute.

earthquake_card.Title: Earthquake Card
earthquake_card.Description: This skill card teaches you Earthquake. Skill Card No. 4.

gnomes_domain_card.Title: Gnome's Domain Card
gnomes_domain_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Gnome's Domain" which targets an area with the power of Sylph to decrease their resistance to air attribute.

raging_storm_card.Title: Raging Storm Card
raging_storm_card.Description: Raging storm will sweep all the enemies around you. Skill Card No. 3

sylphs_playground_card.Title: Sylph's Playground Card
sylphs_playground_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Sylph's Playground" which targets an area with the power of Sylph to decrease their resistance to water attribute.

searing_light_card.Title: Searing Light Card
searing_light_card.Description: Light based magic attack. Arrows from the sky will attack your enemies. Skill Card No. 3.

med._cure_card.Title: Med. Cure Card
med._cure_card.Description: Med. Cure will cure all the beginner and medium status affecting skills. Skill Card No. 5.

sacred_oath_card.Title: Sacred Oath Card
sacred_oath_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the 'Sacred Oath' which grants it's light to everyone in the party through the casters increased faith.

celestial_strike_card.Title: Celestial Strike Card
celestial_strike_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the 'Celestial Strike' to cast a Light based attribute attack.

staff_of_agony_card.Title: Staff of Agony Card
staff_of_agony_card.Description: Dark based magic attack. Scales based on the Dark Attribute stats of the equipment. Skill Card No.4.

scythe_card.Title: Scythe Card
scythe_card.Description: Dark based magic attack. The Grim Reaper will be summoned and attack your enemies. Skill Card No. 12.

fear_card.Title: Fear Card
fear_card.Description: Fear can be used with Scythe to render Power-Type skills and regular attacks useless for a limited amount of time. Skill Card No. 2.

dark_commando_card.Title: Dark Commando Card
dark_commando_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches you 'Dark Commando' to deal an additional Dark based attribute attack.

ghostly_whisper_card.Title: Ghostly Whisper Card
ghostly_whisper_card.Description: Card No. 12 teaches the "Ghostly Whisper" which targets enemies with a dark presence to take damage over time.

steel_punch_skill_card.Title: Steel Punch (Skill) Card
steel_punch_skill_card.Description: Steel Punch strikes the enemy with power of cold thick steel.

shockwave_card.Title: Shockwave Card
shockwave_card.Description: Card No. 3, which gives the "Shockwave" skill used to gather including the smallest and make a big blow.

bulls_eye_card.Title: Bull's Eye Card
bulls_eye_card.Description: Card No.4 teaches the "Bull's Eye" skill. It increases Attack Accuracy by enhancing concentration for a certain period of time.

burning_rave_card.Title: Burning Rave Card
burning_rave_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the "Burning Rave" skill. It creates an endless fighting spirit to continuously attack the enemy.

shockvibe_card.Title: Shockvibe Card
shockvibe_card.Description: Card No. 10 teaches the "Shockvibe" skill. It reduces Attack Accuracy of the opponent for a certain period of time as it strikes the enemy's head to cause dizziness.

sense_breaker_card.Title: Sense Breaker Card
sense_breaker_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Sense Breaker" skill. It reduces the Sensing Power of the enemy for a certain period of time by distracting it.

luck_breaker_card.Title: Luck Breaker Card
luck_breaker_card.Description: Card No. 5 teaches the "Luck Breaker" skill. It reduces the enemy' luck for a certain period of time.

pumping_heart_card.Title: Pumping Heart Card
pumping_heart_card.Description: Card No. 6 teaches the "Pumping Heart" skill. It increases Party member's Attack Power for a certain period of time by adjusting My heart beat to that of fellow soldiers', boosting morale.

armor_breaker_card.Title: Armor Breaker Card
armor_breaker_card.Description: Card No. 9 teaches the "Armor Breaker" skill. It makes the battle more favorable for a certain time by decreasing the enemy's Defense Power.

upper_smash_card.Title: Upper Smash Card
upper_smash_card.Description: Card No. 3 teaches "Upper Smash skill". It hits the enemy and hits again when the enemy falls to the ground.

hyper_beat_card.Title: Hyper Beat Card
hyper_beat_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the "Hyper Beat" skill. It increases My speed for a certain period of time as it increases the level of muscle tension to speed up the reaction time.

tornado_bomb_card.Title: Tornado Bomb Card
tornado_bomb_card.Description: Card No. 2 teaches "Tornado Bomb". It uses fists with strong turning force causing whirlwinds to attack the enemy.

guard_break_card.Title: Guard Break Card
guard_break_card.Description: Card No.8 teaches "Guard Break" skill. An assisting skill for Shockwave. The skill is useful when using your Devoted Energy as its effect on the enemy is more than just that of Guard Break.

dash_card.Title: Dash Card
dash_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches the "Dash" skill. With the skill, you can approach the enemy even before they see you coming.

uppercut_card.Title: Uppercut Card
uppercut_card.Description: Card No.10 teaches the "Uppercut" skill. this skill uses stored energy to uppercut the enemy into the air.

quad_punch_card.Title: Quad Punch Card
quad_punch_card.Description: Teaches the skill Quad Punch. It lands 4 consecutive blazing blows.

counter_punch_card.Title: Counter Punch Card
counter_punch_card.Description: This card teaches "Counter Punch", the ultimate self-sacrificing technique in boxing. If it does work, you'll deal a lot of damage. When you are using "Uppercut", this skill will activate automatically.

eagle_eye_card.Title: Eagle Eye Card
eagle_eye_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Eagle Eye" which increases AC. It affects the player and the party as well.

guard_card.Title: Guard Card
guard_card.Description: Card No. 13 teaches "Guard" skill. It uses the quick movements of the user to guard themselves against powerful attacks.

tetra_punch_card.Title: Tetra Punch Card
tetra_punch_card.Description: Card No.12 teaches the "Tetra Punch" where players can do four consecutive blows to the enemy's critical spot.

desperate_rally_card.Title: Desperate Rally Card
desperate_rally_card.Description: Card No.4 teaches you the skill Desperate rally which will bring out the best in a warrior in dire situations.

flash_cut_card.Title: Flash Cut Card
flash_cut_card.Description: This card teaches you Flash Cut to strike your enemies fast. Skill Card No. 5.

adrenaline_card.Title: Adrenaline Card
adrenaline_card.Description: This skill will increase your AP temporarily. Skill Card No.11

flaming_fist_card.Title: Flaming Fist Card
flaming_fist_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the 'Flaming Fist' which lets you attack an enemy with your burning fighting spirit.

mega_flash_cut_card.Title: Mega Flash Cut Card
mega_flash_cut_card.Description: Card No. 11 teaches the skill "Mega Flash Cut" which strikes your enemy really quickly.

faint_card.Title: Faint Card
faint_card.Description: Card No.8 teaches the "Faint" skill. An assisting skill for Shockwave skill. Faint status effects will often be given to an enemy when using Shockwave.

lacerator_card.Title: Lacerator Card
lacerator_card.Description: Card No.4 teaches the "Lacerator" skill. It slashes enemies that are in the front but at the same time attacks ones that are behind in a straight slashing motion.

berserker_card.Title: Berserker Card
berserker_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches the "Berserker" skill. This skill releases all the anger deep within the soul to raise attack power while sacrificing one's own HP and MP.

piercing_wave_card.Title: Piercing Wave Card
piercing_wave_card.Description: Teaches the skill Piercing Wave. It channels the energy inside one's body and shoot's it to the enemy.

aura_of_haste_card.Title: Aura of Haste Card
aura_of_haste_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Aura of Haste" that lowers the DX of the user and the user's party members.

tidal_slash_card.Title: Tidal Slash Card
tidal_slash_card.Description: You will be able to slice water in half with "Tidal Slash."

earthquake_blade_card.Title: Earthquake Blade Card
earthquake_blade_card.Description: Card No.7 teaches you Earthquake Blade which attacks enemies with incredible shockwaves.

blazing_strike_card.Title: Blazing Strike Card
blazing_strike_card.Description: This card teaches the skill "Blazing Strike" that delivers devastating blows with blazing speed.

inferno_blade_card.Title: Inferno Blade Card
inferno_blade_card.Description: Card No.5 teaches the "Inferno Blade" skill. This skill summons a sword of fire to attack the surrounding enemies.

tempest_strike_card.Title: Tempest Strike Card
tempest_strike_card.Description: Card No.9 teaches "Tempest Strike" where players can create sharp circular wind motions around them to slash their enemy.

shadow_skill_card.Title: Shadow (Skill) Card
shadow_skill_card.Description: Shadow will create an illusion that attacks from multiple angles. Skill Card No. 12.

suffocate_card.Title: Suffocate Card
suffocate_card.Description: Suffocate will reveal hidden enemies. It also renders your enemy unable to breath. Skill Card No. 4.

sonic_slash_card.Title: Sonic Slash Card
sonic_slash_card.Description: Sonic Slash will rupture your enemy's eardrums. Skill Card No. 13.

gale_strike_card.Title: Gale Strike Card
gale_strike_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches you Gale Strike which is an advanced form of Tempest Strike.

chi_sword_card.Title: Chi Sword.gif Card
chi_sword_card.Description: Card No. 4 teaches the 'Chi Sword' which fills the sword with chi to make it bigger.
